<paragraph blockId="257.[151,1436,942,1329]" pageId="257" pageNumber="258">
REMARKS: 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[270,495,1122,1150]" pageId="257" pageNumber="258" refId="ref368401" refString="Rondani, C. (1857) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol: II. Species italicae ordinis dipterorum in genera characteribus definita, ordinatim collectae, methodo analitica distinctae, et novis vel minus cognitis descriptis. Pars prima. Oestridae: Syrphfidae [sic!]: Conopidae. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma], 264 pp., 1 pl. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 8160" type="book" year="1857">Rondani (1857: 63)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1857" box="[624,889,1123,1149]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Merodon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="257" pageNumber="258" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="submetallicus">
<emphasis box="[624,889,1123,1149]" italics="true" pageId="257" pageNumber="258">Merodon submetallicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from just the male sex, without specifying the exact 
<taxonomicName box="[267,353,1159,1185]" family="Number" pageId="257" pageNumber="26" rank="family">number</taxonomicName>
of specimens and not giving a range of lengths, from material received from 
<collectingCountry box="[1249,1353,1159,1185]" name="Germany" pageId="257" pageNumber="258">Germany</collectingCountry>
and L. Bellardi. We could not locate any 
<typeStatus box="[577,625,1195,1221]" pageId="257" pageNumber="258">type</typeStatus>
specimens during this study. Not included in the 
<typeStatus box="[1174,1222,1195,1221]" pageId="257" pageNumber="258">type</typeStatus>
series are a MZUF male and a MSNC male from “Apenn. [= Apennines]” because it is not the 
<typeStatus box="[1034,1082,1231,1257]" pageId="257" pageNumber="258">type</typeStatus>
locality, a female because of its sex, a MZUF male numbered “63” dated “1869”, which is subsequent to the original description, and a MSNC specimen because it is not from the 
<typeStatus box="[601,649,1303,1329]" pageId="257" pageNumber="258">type</typeStatus>
locality.
</paragraph>
